RT @TheWpgChamber: To start us off, @iwadood addresses when and why should organizations engage a partner. Wadood drawing on extensive expe…
Thank you for tuning in to @TheWpgChamber #BOLD radio on @680CJOB Please contact @bluecanvasgroup @Third_Quarter @Protegra to talk further!
'Understand your value proposition. If you can't deliver on it because you are too fragmented, will lose clients' Sue Barkman @Third_Quarter
'No one can do & be an expert in everything themselves. Make sure to select right help' @iwadood @bluecanvasgroup @TheWpgChamber @680CJOB
'Trust critical in partnership. They should bring up issues you're not expert in. Why you have engaged them as partner' @WendieKarlowsky
'Set expectations early & manage them continuously. This often leads to breakdown in quality of delivery. Fix issue then move on' @iwadood
'Determine who you are really & what is your brand when deciding when & with whom to engage as partner' Sue Barkman @Third_Quarter @680CJOB
'Often when relationships go sour don't come as a surprise. Due to events that preceded break up' @WendieKarlowsky @bluecanvasgroup @680CJOB
'Good communications important throughout relationship w/ partner & deal with things right away' Sue Barkman @Third_Quarter @TheWpgChamber
'Misconceptions of partnerships: more expensive to engage partner & should just do tasks myself; being able to trust a partner' @iwadood
'Take accountability & apologize for problem then fix problem. Doesn't often happen payroll industry' @WendieKarlowsky @bluecanvasgroup
'We have always partnered with other orgs. Key is select RIGHT partner to help grow your biz. Will have happy employees & clients' @iwadood
'Breaking up with partner is hard to do if invested time & effort. Sometimes need to take break' Sue Barkman @Third_Quarter @TheWpgChamber
'When we ask clients to be our partner, we take time to find out their needs & jobs to be done. They trust us.' - Sue Barkman @Third_Quarter
'When tasks are not part of your core biz, you don't know what you don't know.  Bring in partner w/ expertise' @iwadood @TheWpgChamber
'Getting paid accurately has major impact on employees. @bluecanvasgroup we like to do things right. Payroll not grey area' @WendieKarlowsky
'Protegra focuses on creating solutions driven by software & innovating. We created @bluecanvasgroup - payroll & work mgmt company' @iwadood
'We lose credibility if our employees are not paid properly, so found another #LEGO block. We partnered w/ @bluecanvasgroup' @Third_Quarter
'We looked @ everything we did. We put all jobs as biz on whiteboard & decided we wanted to find payroll partner' Sue Barkman @Third_Quarter
'A good partner should want to help you, provide good value & expertise, bring things to light' @WendieKarlowsky @bluecanvasgroup @680CJOB
'Good partnerships are like #LEGO - it has to fit. Should just flow, like your partner works right in your biz' Sue Barkman @Third_Quarter
'We rely completely on partners so we can focus on what we do best rather than doing extraneous tasks' Sue Barkman @Third_Quarter @680CJOB
Look @ opportunity costs. Are you spending time on things taking you away from delivering value to customers & generating more customers?
'Look for partners to deliver services not expert in & focus on what you do best. Often more professionally done, cost effective.' @iwadood
Should 1st look @ jobs to be done by biz  including core competencies before engaging partner @iwadood @bluecanvasgroup @TheWpgChamber
